    "description": "Deflect powerful monsters to progress through the game using simple mechanics.<br><br>+Challenging levels with puzzle elements.<br><br>+THERES NO SAVE. With the expectancy of a 40 minutes playthrough. Lowered to around 10 minutes if you get good.<br><br>    Use &quot;GUST&quot; to slow enemies down and move obstacles, extinguish packs of monsters with &quot;FLAMES&quot; and damage long range targets with &quot;ICELANCE&quot;. Don't forget that everything is stronger, faster or neverending, so main goal is to run and reach the end as fast as possible.<br><br>*This is an indie project. If you like pay once play forever type of games with cool mechanics, SUPPORT US, we are doing a longer project!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161410/extras/aaec74d891d819f4751a826a9ca508ed.poster.avif?t=1672498935\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161410/extras/aaec74d891d819f4751a826a9ca508ed.webm?t=1672498935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161410/extras/aaec74d891d819f4751a826a9ca508ed.mp4?t=1672498935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>She euthanized a lot, helping desperately sick people die. So she was exiled to the land infested by the demons.<br>Fighting was mostly futile but her spells Gust, Scorch and Icicle were helpful.<br>She was not expected to survive it as it was her punishment for euthanizing sick countrymen, taking gods gift in unnatural ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161410/extras/55dce09c64c3314cecb931c395d94c92.poster.avif?t=1672498935\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/